items.name: 莆仙戏Lora ，PuXian Opera，興化劇
items.description:
触发关键词：Opera Pheasant Tail， puxian opera, dan role

trigger words: Opera Pheasant Tail， puxian opera, dan role,

トリガーワード:Opera Pheasant Tail， puxian opera, dan role,

莆仙戏（旧称“兴化戏” ），福建省莆田市传统地方戏曲剧种，是中国现存古老剧种之一。莆仙戏源于唐、成于宋、盛于明清，流行于古称兴化的莆田、仙游二县及闽中、闽南的兴化方言地区，现仍保留不少宋元南戏音乐元素，被誉为“宋元南戏的活化石”。莆仙戏表演古朴优雅，综合了莆仙的民间歌谣俚曲、十音八乐、宋元词曲的艺术特点，用方言演唱，具有浓厚的地方色彩。

我从小坐着我爷爷的自行车走街串巷看莆仙戏，吃街边刚出锅的葱油饼和热腾腾的扁食，可惜现在这些温馨回忆已经一去不回头，我希望找回这些消逝的记忆，希望用ai的方式让更多人了解莆仙戏，让世界各地的人都可以使用lora模型来创建他们喜欢的莆仙戏剧人物。

I grew up sitting on my grandfather’s bicycle, walking around the streets to watch Puxian Opera, and eating freshly baked scallion pancakes and hot flat dumplings. Unfortunately, these warm memories are gone now. I wish to use AI to make more people from whole world know Puxian Opera, and people all over the world can use the lora model to create their favorite Puxian opera characters.

子供の頃、祖父の自転車に乗って興化劇を観に行き、焼きたてのネギチヂミや熱々の平らな餃子を食べました。この温かい思い出がもうなくなってしまうのは残念だ。失われた思い出を見つけたいと思っています。だから、AI を使用して、より多くの人に興化劇について知ってもらい、世界中の人々が AI loraを使用してお気に入りの興化劇のキャラクターを作成できるを願っています。

items.description:

如您有模型定制或其他合作、咨询需求，请联系Wechat: pomelonioi。请简单注明来意，时间宝贵不闲聊哈，谢谢理解！

If you have any model customization or other collaboration and consultation needs, please contact Wechat: pomelonioi . Kindly provide a brief description of your inquiry, as there's limited time and no time for casual chats. Thank you!

This is a model with a slight wide-angle lens effect from an upward shooting perspective. Shooting from bottom to top at an extreme angle creates a distortion effect, making the lower part appear wider and the upper part narrower.

The higher the Lora weight and the steeper the upward shooting angle, the more pronounced the distortion effect becomes. The resulting image appears more grandiose and delivers a strong visual impact. This effect is well-suited for capturing tall buildings and natural landscapes. It also adds a striking visual impact to portrait photography, creating the impression of "long legs," "shoes close to the lens," and "a very tall person with a small face."

Currently, the perspective shifts are achieved using tags like "from below" or "from above," but these terms are too vague, only slightly offsetting the view "up" or "down." They do not provide the desired sense of extending the image or the necessary distortion effect, especially when shooting from an extremely low angle, placing the lens on the floor, or aiming it at the feet and shoes.

(1) Base Model: Inkshadow Moyourenzaoren

(2) Trigger Word: extremeangle

(3) Recommended Weight: 1.0 or 0.75

(4) When generating characters, the model with a high weight tends to produce full-body images, so remember to use adetailer. Half-body images also work well. There are no particular restrictions when generating buildings and landscapes.

这是带有一点点广角镜头效果的仰拍视角模型，从下而上的仰拍视角会造成下宽上窄的畸变效果。

Lora权重越高、仰拍角度越大、畸变效果越明显、画面更显高大宏伟、给人的视觉冲击力也越强。它既适合高大建筑、自然风光的呈现；又会给人像摄影带来强烈的“大长腿”、“鞋子怼镜头”、“人很高、脸很小”的视觉冲击。

目前视角的切换都是用from below、from above等tag，而这些词的含义过于泛泛，只是稍微“往下”或者“往上”偏移一点，无法得到我想要的画面延伸感，也没有该有的畸变效果，更别说这种镜头放在地板上、怼在脚和鞋子上拍摄的极低视角了。

（1）训练底模：墨幽人造人v1040

（2）触发词：extremeangle

（3）建议权重：1.0或者0.75

（4）生成人物时模型高权重倾向于全身图，一定要记得开adetailer；半身图亦有不错的效果；生成建筑和风景时无所谓；

Request or Suggestion Rule:

  1. No request for a minor!

  2. The requested should have public data (not private)

  3. Should have more than 30 good-quality images

  4. Since all requests or suggestions are free, I will still need to like your request, otherwise its a work not a hobby for me.

  5. Be a decent human being and leave a review if your request is up It takes you only 5 mins while it takes me hours, electricity, and effort to do your requests.

NOTE: I will keep updating more actresses in versions update

===

Usage Guide

--

A. Lora Weight

  • 0.1 ~ 0.4 -- is to combine multiple faces or features, or if you experience overbaking

  • 0.5 ~ 0.7 -- is a balanced weight to get still accurate features but with more flexibility

  • 0.8 ~ 1.0 -- is to create an accurate representation of the features.

B. CFG Scale

  • A lower CFG Scale means AI gets more creative and less overbaking problems.

  • A higher CFG Scale means results get very accurate with training sets and are more prone to overbaking problems.

  • Dynamic CFG Threshold, using this method allows you to bump up quality and achieve photorealistic quickly, but with lycoris, I found out recently that this method actually lowers the success rate, so only use it when you are composing with a Lora / model that works fine with this method.

C. Sampling Steps, High Res Fix & Upscaling

  • I like sampling steps at 50, with high res steps at 20, or 1/2 of the sampling steps.

  • I find that 2M Karras works better and faster than SDE Karras. with ERSGAN 4x+ method + ERSGAN 4x for Upscaling. This method actually gives quite good results without being too sharp or too plasticky

  • Upscaling - GPFGAN @0.25, Codeformer @0.3 & Codeformer Weight @0.15 seems to yield superior results.

Enjoy.

HappyDiffusion FX is the default model developed for HappyDiffusion, focused on generating ultra realistic images.

Features

• Ultra-Realism: We have carefully handpicked and merged over 20 realistic models on Civitai to create HappyDiffsuion FX. 

• Meticulously Trained: We've put in considerable effort, testing hundreds of prompts to ensure the best possible outcomes. After going through several iterations, we have learned how to perfectly train the model to attain images that look lifelike.

• Extensively Refined: A lot of labor of love has been put into refining the final results and training the model.

License

items.name: Nadine Breaty
items.description:
A request of @psytrancehero.

Nadine Breaty is a German social media influencer with around 11M followers on TikTok.

140-step TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with these settings.

Fair warning: Most models I've tested this TI with can't deal with her hair, especially for longer shots. On top of that, that streak of white hair seems to make the AI interpret sometimes that Nadine is an elder woman, which is a bit infuriating. Overall, I'd recommend sticking to closer shots when using this TI.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Do you have a specific idea for a TI in mind? Visit my website and let me know.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of beautiful (nadbreaty:0.99), a woman with beautiful hair, hair upsweep updo, as a movie star in a (movie premiere), premiere gala, (near a movie theatre), natural skin texture, (elegant {red|yellow|blue|green|black|turquoise} sweater off-shoulder with suspenders), 24mm, 4k textures, soft cinematic light, adobe lightroom, photolab, hdr, intricate, elegant, highly detailed, sharp focus, ((((cinematic look)))), soothing tones, insane details, intricate details, hyperdetailed, low contrast, soft cinematic light, exposure blend, hdr, faded, (paparazzi in background), (painted lips:1.1), ((looking straight at the camera:1.1)), (smiling)"

items.name: gladiia/グレイディーア/歌蕾蒂娅 (Arknights)
items.description:
• THIS MODEL HAS TWO FILES. YOU NEED TO USE THEM TOGETHER!!!
  • The associated trigger words are only for reference, it may need to be adjusted at some times.
  • The recommended weight for the embedding model is 1, which provides higher fidelity; if greater generalization is needed, it can be lowered to 0.5. The recommended weight for the LoRA model is 0.85.

How to Use This Model

THIS MODEL HAS TWO FILES. YOU NEED TO USE THEM TOGETHER!!!. In this case, you need to download both gladiia_arknights.pt and gladiia_arknights.safetensors, then use gladiia_arknights.pt as texture inversion embedding, and use gladiia_arknights.safetensors as LoRA at the same time.

このモデルには2つのファイルがあります。一緒に使う必要があります！！！。 この場合、gladiia_arknights.ptとgladiia_arknights.safetensorsの両方をダウンロード する必要があります。gladiia_arknights.ptをテクスチャ反転埋め込みとして使用し、同時にgladiia_arknights.safetensorsをLoRAとして使用してください。

这个模型有两个文件。你需要同时使用它们！！！。 在这种情况下，您需要下载gladiia_arknights.pt和gladiia_arknights.safetensors这两个文件，然后将gladiia_arknights.pt用作纹理反转嵌入， 同时使用gladiia_arknights.safetensors作为LoRA。

이 모델은 두 개의 파일이 있습니다. 두 파일을 함께 사용해야 합니다!!!. 이 경우에는 gladiia_arknights.pt와 gladiia_arknights.safetensors 두 파일을 모두 다운로드하신 다음에 gladiia_arknights.pt을 텍스처 반전 임베딩으로 사용하고, 동시에 gladiia_arknights.safetensors을 LoRA로 사용하셔야 합니다.

(Translated with ChatGPT)

The trigger word is gladiia_arknights, and the recommended tags are best quality, masterpiece, highres, solo, {gladiia_arknights:1.15}, red_eyes, pointy_ears, long_hair, white_hair, ascot, grey_hair, white_ascot, hair_over_one_eye, black_headwear, hat, bangs, breasts.

How This Model Is Trained

This model is trained with HCP-Diffusion. And the auto-training framework is maintained by DeepGHS Team.

Why Some Preview Images Not Look Like Gladiia Arknights

All the prompt texts used on the preview images (which can be viewed by clicking on the images) are automatically generated using clustering algorithms based on feature information extracted from the training dataset. The seed used during image generation is also randomly generated, and the images have not undergone any selection or modification. As a result, there is a possibility of the mentioned issues occurring.

In practice, based on our internal testing, most models that experience such issues perform better in actual usage than what is seen in the preview images. The only thing you may need to do is adjusting the tags you are using.

I Felt This Model May Be Overfitting or Underfitting, What Shall I Do

Our model has been published on huggingface repository - CyberHarem/gladiia_arknights, where models of all the steps are saved. Also, we published the training dataset on huggingface dataset - CyberHarem/gladiia_arknights, which may be helpful to you.

Why Not Just Using The Better-Selected Images

Our model's entire process, from data crawling, training, to generating preview images and publishing, is 100% automated without any human intervention. It's an interesting experiment conducted by our team, and for this purpose, we have developed a complete set of software infrastructure, including data filtering, automatic training, and automated publishing. Therefore, if possible, we would appreciate more feedback or suggestions as they are highly valuable to us.

Why Can't the Desired Character Outfits Be Accurately Generated

Our current training data is sourced from various image websites, and for a fully automated pipeline, it's challenging to accurately predict which official images a character possesses. Consequently, outfit generation relies on clustering based on labels from the training dataset in an attempt to achieve the best possible recreation. We will continue to address this issue and attempt optimization, but it remains a challenge that cannot be completely resolved. The accuracy of outfit recreation is also unlikely to match the level achieved by manually trained models.

In fact, this model's greatest strengths lie in recreating the inherent characteristics of the characters themselves and its relatively strong generalization capabilities, owing to its larger dataset. As such, this model is well-suited for tasks such as changing outfits, posing characters, and, of course, generating NSFW images of characters!😉".

For the following groups, it is not recommended to use this model and we express regret:

  1. Individuals who cannot tolerate any deviations from the original character design, even in the slightest detail.
  2. Individuals who are facing the application scenarios with high demands for accuracy in recreating character outfits.
  3. Individuals who cannot accept the potential randomness in AI-generated images based on the Stable Diffusion algorithm.
  4. Individuals who are not comfortable with the fully automated process of training character models using LoRA, or those who believe that training character models must be done purely through manual operations to avoid disrespecting the characters.
  5. Individuals who finds the generated image content offensive to their values.

items.name: Opentoe heels/sandals with legwears XL
items.description:
The Lora model is trained to show different kind of opentoe shoewears (opentoe high heels, sandals) paired with legwears (pantyhose, stockings).

The XL version is trained using an improved set of SD 1.5 version.

The XL Lora improvements include:

-          More detailed particulars like nyloned toes;

-          Improved nylon rendering also with sheer tan nylon (the most difficult one).

The model is trained with tan color legwears, so with no specifications probably the output will be a leg with tan color legwear. Anyway the model was tested also with other lora models specific for black or white legwears.

WARNING: The details level of Lora could drop in case of full body portraits (very little heels) or in case of many different Lora used together. Details can be rescued using inpaint algorithm only on feet, with a very specific description of opentoe heels, better if after an upscale.

Triggering LORA keyword:

opentoeNYX

There are different kinds of sandals, that can be triggered using for example ankle straps, twisted ankle straps, and the color of shoewear could be easily changed.

New optional keywords :

-          twisted ankle straps

-          ornated front straps

-          natural toenails

-          painted toenails

Lora weight:

A value about 1 is reccomended.

In the prompt, to trigger sandals may be useful a 1.2-1.3 keyword weight.

This Lora could be used both with realistic or manga checkpoints.

Final statements:

1. You are solely responsible for any creative work using this model.

2. You cannot use this model to intentionally produce or share illegal images or content.

3. Furthermore can't use this model for malicious, hurtful, defamatory, fraudulent or political purposes.
